comments: Tate (HOU) extends his arms and initiates contact to Middleton (MIL) that affects his FOM.
Lopez (MIL) and Tate (HOU) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Holiday (MIL) places his hand to Porter Jr.'s (HOU) front during the pick and marginal contact occurs.
Holiday (MIL) legally contests Porter Jr. (HOU) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Lopez (MIL) and Tate (HOU) engage and disengage with one another off ball prior to the on the ball screen.
Lopez (MIL) makes marginal contact to Porter Jr.'s (HOU) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Holiday (MIL) places his arm to Porter Jr.'s (HOU) front during his drive and contact affects his SQBR.
Porter Jr. (HOU) maintains legal guarding position on Lopez (MIL) as body contact occurs in the post.
Tate (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in Holiday's (MIL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Tucker (MIL) places his hand to Tate's (HOU) backside after gathering the pass and marginal contact occurs during his shot attempt at the basket.
Holiday (MIL) makes marginal contact to Olynyk (HOU) contesting his shot attempt at the basket.
Tucker (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Wilson's (HOU) and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Wood's (HOU) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Tate (HOU) makes brief contact to Middleton's (MIL) arm at the start of his drive and he is able to move through the marginal contact.
Tate (HOU) makes marginal contact to Middleton's (MIL) front after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Tucker (MIL) places a resting hand to Olynyk's (HOU) side after gathering the pass and dislodges the ball before incidental contact occurs.

Tucker (MIL) and Forbes (MIL) have their hands on the ball and tie up Olynyk (HOU) and a held ball is whistled.  Houston signals for a timeout, but the held ball is whistled before it is acknowledged.
Olynyk (HOU) gathers the ball with control and does not tap it during the jump ball.
Tucker (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Wilson's (HOU) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Porter Jr. (HOU) makes marginal contact to Holiday's (MIL) hand after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Tate (HOU) and Lopez (MIL) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Lopez (MIL) commits a take foul on Porter Jr. (HOU).
Middleton (MIL) does not establish himself in bounds prior to gathering the pass.
